ers的新区域于5月16日开放，“替代城市V1”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Horo Arthophone新区域“替代城市V1”于5月16日开业-P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024/embed/#?secret=gI5Iy37xdl#?secret=2CGs5DpuLk" data-secret="2CGs5DpuLk" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="px4b9y68O5"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-became-the-first-vtuber-agency-and-group-in-history-to-reach-90-million-total-youtube-channel-subscribers/">Horo Live Production Vtuber办公室 /集团的第一个总渠道有9000万注册人</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Horo Live Productions VTUBER办公室 /集团的第一个总渠道编号为9000万注册人” -P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-became-the-first-vtuber-agency-and-group-in-history-to-reach-90-million-total-youtube-channel-subscribers/embed/#?secret=hUvfXJlaN2#?secret=px4b9y68O5" data-secret="px4b9y68O5" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p> <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000001041.000030268.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="媒体组合项目“ Hololive”的“神奇女孩Holo Witch！”已经开始了！主PV和关键视觉效果立即发布！">媒体组合项目“ Hololive”的“神奇女孩Holo Witch！”已经开始了！主PV和关键视觉效果立即发布！</a></p><cite>公关时报</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p> <a href="https://holowitches.hololivepro.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="神奇的女孩Holo女巫！">神奇的女孩Holo女巫！</a> / <a href="https://x.com/holoWitches" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="神奇的女孩霍洛希[官方]">魔法女孩霍洛希[官方]</a></p> <cite>Horo Live Production / X（Twitter）</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>p2y.jp管理代表“ 2”</em> /虚拟 /元 / vtuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="2iHNLAaofD"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/magical-girl-holowitches-a-hololive-media-mix-project-released-main-pv-etc/">“神奇的女孩Holowitches！”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“神奇的女孩Holowitches！”" src="https://en.p2y.jp/magical-girl-holowitches-a-hololive-media-mix-project-released-main-pv-etc/embed/#?secret=oIm3cVLkAX#?secret=2iHNLAaofD" data-secret="2iHNLAaofD" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> Horo Live<a href="https://p2y.jp">的</a><a href="https://p2y.jp/magical-girl-holowitches-a-hololive-media-mix-project-released-main-pv-etc/">媒体混音项目“ Magical Girl Hollowich！”</a></content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://p2y.jp/magical-girl-holowitches-a-hololive-media-midia-mix-mix-mix-mix-mix-proseared-main-pv-feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 125485</post-id></item><item><title> RK音乐新人虚拟歌手Neun / Culua / Meda首次亮相</title><link/>https://p2y.jp/rk-music-newal-singer-neun-culua-and-meda-debut/<comments> https://p2y.jp/rk-music-new-virtual-new-new-new-neun-culua-s-s-and-meda-debut/#respondond</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[p2y_admin Wed, 15 May 2024 05:47:41 +0000 VTuberバーチャル音楽CULUA(カルア)MEDA(メダ)NEUN(ノイン)RK MusicTwitterYouTubeYouTuberバーチャルYouTuberバーチャルシンガーヒゲドライバー新人VTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=125438 <p> RK Music Co.，Ltd。2024年5月14日（Siwa 6），新秀虚拟歌手（Noin），Culua（Kalua）和三个Debi（Meda）Debi（Meda）Devil […]。</p>帖子<a href="https://p2y.jp/rk-music-new-virtual-singer-neun-culua-and-meda-debut/">RK音乐新人虚拟歌手Neun / Culua / Meda首次亮相</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">p2y.jp</a> 。]>; </des